{"parentUuid":"194d2574-da81-489b-a203-94b2efebdaa5","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01UwxzFW98J8gE1P9iq34W22","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"`radial-gradient` は CSS の関数で、中心点から外側に向かって放射状に色が変化するグラデーションを生成します。\n\n## 基本構文\n\n```css\nbackground: radial-gradient(shape size at position, color1, color2, ...);\n```\n\n## 例\n\n```css\n/* 中心が白、外側が黒 */\nbackground: radial-gradient(white, black);\n\n/* 円形、中心が赤、外側が青 */\nbackground: radial-gradient(circle, red, blue);\n\n/* 位置指定（左上を中心に） */\nbackground: radial-gradient(circle at top left, red, blue);\n\n/* 色の停止点を指定 */\nbackground: radial-gradient(circle, red 0%, yellow 50%, blue 100%);\n```\n\n## shape（形状）\n\n| 値 | 説明 |\n|---|---|\n| `ellipse`（デフォルト） | 楕円形 |\n| `circle` | 正円形 |\n\n## よく使うパターン\n\n```css\n/* スポットライト効果 */\nbackground: radial-gradient(circle at center, rgba(255,255,255,0.3), transparent);\n\n/* 複数のグラデーションを重ねる */\nbackground: \n  radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, red, transparent),\n  radial-gradient(circle at 70% 70%, blue, transparent);\n```\n\n`linear-gradient`（直線）との違いは、広がり方が「直線」か「放射状」かという点です。"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":6359,"cache_read_input_tokens":10932,"output_tokens":450,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":6359,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CZifHBX6QNuRChPSQJh1j","type":"assistant","uuid":"c6500363-e930-408e-8810-3c4dae608258","timestamp":"2026-04-04T11:35:07.551Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/haru/ghq/github.com/harusame0616/ijuku","sessionId":"1f65c573-6f86-466a-92f6-b669dc6ad359","version":"2.1.81","gitBranch":"top"}
